&lt;h2 id="overview"&gt;Overview&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This article verifies that the Hugo multilingual configuration is correct and that i18n translations work properly.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="test-points"&gt;Test Points&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;English content renders correctly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Menu uses i18n to display English names&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Page title and description switch by language&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Archive and search page content is in column 2&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
